{"tid":698604,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[弱x智] 摩迪：我想攞啲獎嚟交換世界盃冠軍","createTime":"2018-06-12T00:07:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T03:32:17.000Z","uid":54373,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9bea0e0e54b1d889d6f8a9dd686bcc1b8e30e952","tid":698604,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T00:07:44.000Z","msg":"皇家馬德里今年再一次在歐聯稱霸，助攻助守不遺餘力的中場大腦莫迪歷居功至偉。可能在皇馬已經贏盡一切，莫迪歷想用一些在皇馬贏得的錦標，換取克羅地亞在世盃取得成功。<br />\n<br />\n莫迪歷在12/13球季由熱刺轉投皇馬，協助球隊贏得一次西甲冠軍、一次西班牙盃冠軍以及四次歐聯冠軍。似在球會經已贏到麻木，莫迪歷想克羅地亞在今年世盃有所作為：「這是一個漫長而且艱苦的球季，我們在西甲以及西盃的表現都不似預期。但到最後我們贏得歐聯冠軍，這是最重要的。我好高興可以成為球會的一份子。但我希望可以用皇馬的一些錦標交換，以換取克羅地亞取得大成功（世盃冠軍）。」"},{"pid":"573d8213f7a9031e7a3039f87a5ed4c42c59f99b","tid":698604,"uid":185656,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T00:14:39.000Z","msg":"Lionel Messi: I would swap Barcelona title for Argentina World Cup success"},{"pid":"7dbf13c9a26c12be519a8ed2bd08b4d81c874add","tid":698604,"uid":186784,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"573d8213f7a9031e7a3039f87a5ed4c42c59f99b","tid":698604,"uid":185656,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T00:14:39.000Z","msg":"Lionel Messi: I would swap Barcelona title for Argentina World Cup success"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T00:34:40.000Z","msg":"弱x智美斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e7938488152a9db01f0a9fed5537e0359460472","tid":698604,"uid":56900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7dbf13c9a26c12be519a8ed2bd08b4d81c874add","tid":698604,"uid":186784,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"573d8213f7a9031e7a3039f87a5ed4c42c59f99b","tid":698604,"uid":185656,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T00:14:39.000Z","msg":"Lionel Messi: I would swap Barcelona title for Argentina World Cup success"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime